meta {
  name: Set Zone Gain (INC)
  type: http
  seq: 2
}

docs {
  SET does not return a +value response — use INC delta instead:

  Command:  INC ZONE-A.GAIN -5
  Response: +ZONE-A.GAIN -15.00
            *INC ZONE-A.GAIN -5

  To set absolute value: read current gain, compute delta, send INC.
  Example: current=-10, target=-15 → INC ZONE-A.GAIN -5.00
}
